  10. Hu3 Chu2-jit8-oh8 kau3-oan5 leng5-siu-hoe7 (3) 
  “To7-siong7-sek e5 kau3-iok8-hoat” 
  1. “To7-siong7” nng7-ji7 e5 i3-gi7
  Lan2 i2-keng chioh Po2-lo5 ti7 Hui-lip8-pi2 sou2 kong2 e5 oe7 kong2, “Ti3-i3 thau5-cheng5 e5 su7, ng3 sou2 chhah e5 pio lai5 chau2, kau3 tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 ti7 Ki-tok Ia5-sou, tui3 teng2-bin7 tiau3 lan2 e5 siuN2.” 
  Ti7 Hi-pek-lai5 12 chiuN kong2, “Chiu7 tioh8 pang3-he7 tak8-ho7 e5 tang7-taN3, kap khoai3-khoai3 tiN5-poaN3 lan2 e5 choe7, eng7 thun-lun2 lai5 chau2 sou2 an-pai5 ti7 lan2 thau5-cheng5 e5 lou7-cham7. Tioh8 chu3-sin5 khoaN3 Ia5-sou, chiu7-si7 choe3 sin3 e5 goan5-thau5 kap chhiaN5-boe2 e5.” 
  Ti7-chia long2 chiong lan2 e5 sin3-giong2 seng-oah8 pi2-pheng7 choe3 chau2-pio, ia7 ji5-chhiaN2 kau3 lan2 (1) tioh8 ng3 teng2-bin7 chau2, (2) tioh8 chu3-sin5 khoaN3 Ia5-sou, (3) tioh8 pang3-sak it-chhe3 e5 tiN5-poaN3, (4) kim2-ki5 siuN2-phin2 si7 Siong7-te3 beh hou7 lan2--e5, (5) koh tioh8 e7 ki3-tit chit8-hang7, chiu7-si7 teh chau2-pio e5 lang5, m7 si7 chhin3-chhai2 lang5 long2 chai7-tiuN5 teh chau2, chiu7-si7 hiah-e5 siu7 tiau3, siu7 keng2-soan2--e5 chiah teh saN-kap chau2, (6) kah u7 siuN2, chiu7 am3-si7 tou5-tiong u7 lok8-ngou2-chia2, siuN2 bo5 tioh8 e5, (7) koan-chiong3 e5 cheng3-jin5 si7 chhin-chhiuN7 hun5 ui5 lan2 e5 che7 teh khoaN3, (8) hit-e5 chhai5-phoaN3-chia2 si7 Chu2 pun2-sin, an2-ni si7 kek8 kong-to7 koh giam5-cheng3--e5. 
  TaN ti7-chia lan2 chiu7 chai “to7-siong7” kau3-iok8 e5 i3-gi7. Lan2 e5 hak8-seng, pi7 kau3-iok8-chia2, pi2-pheng7 in choe3 chham-ka chau2 e5 sio2 peng5-iu2, in chiu7-si7 ng3 teng2-bin7 teh chau2, ng3-bang7 beh tit-tioh8 teng2-bin7 e5 siuN2--e5. TaN lan2 choe3 lau7-su e5 thang kong2 chiu7-si7 in sai3-phau2 e5 to7-su. Lan2 chit8-bin7 na2 phoaN7 in chau2, m7 si7 the3 in chau2, ia7 be7 tit aiN7 in chau2, si7 phoaN7 in chau2, lai5 ka7 in ka3, chi2-to7 chau2 e5 hong-hoat, pun2-sin ia7 chau2 hou7 in khoaN3, koh chou7 in e5 taN2, tui3 piN-a2 kou2-le7 ka7 in ka-iu5, hou7 in ke-thiN jiat8-sim lai5 ng3 teng2-bin7 e5 kim2-ki5 lai5 chau2. 
  ChaiN2-iuN7 kong2 chong-kau3 kau3-iok8 si7 “to7-siong7” kau3-iok8 hoat te7-it ho2? Chhi3-siuN7 li2 kiam2 e7 eng7-tit eng7 to5-ia2 e5 hong-sek, lai5 nge7 chhih8 hak8-seng hou7 i chiaN5-choe3 chit8 e5 sim2-mih8 bou5-heng5 e5 sin3-giong2-tek e5 jin5-but8, tek8-piat8 tui3 ti7 “sin3-giong2 si7 chu7-iu5--e5.” Siong7-te3 tou chun-tiong7 lang5 e5 chu7-iu5 soan2-tek8 e5 i3-chi3, hong7-kiam3 lau7-su, li2 u7 sim2-mih8 leng5-lek8, thang tui3 ti7 sin3-giong2 lai5 kiong5-che3 to5-ia2 nih? A2-si7, li2 kiam2 e7-tit tui3 ji5-tong5 e5 lai7-bin7 eng7 khe2-hoat, thiu chhut sim2-mih8 ho2 lai5 chou7-tiong5 hou7 i khah seng5 Chu2, soa3 e7 tit-tioh8 kiu3. Seng3-chheh lai7 kiam2 m7 si7 kong2 lian5 poaN3 e5 ho2 lang5 to bo5? Li2 beh tui3 hak8-seng, pi7 kau3-iok8-chia2 e5 lai7-bin7 thiu chhut sim2-mih8 ho2, lai5 khe2-hoat--i ah? Bo5 lah. 
  Li2 tioh8 thiaN Chu2 e5 hoan-hu3, chhi7 I e5 iuN5-a2-kiaN2. Chiu7-si7 li2 oh8 Chu2 choe3 bok8-chia2 chhoa7 I e5 iuN5-a2-kiaN2 kau3 I e5 oah8-chui2-piN, kau3 chhiN-chhui3 e5 chhau2-pou, hou7 in ti7 hia thang tui3 Chu2 lai5 hiong2-siu7 I hong-seng7 leng5-tek8 e5 un-su3, che si7 te7-it ho2 e5. 
  Goa2 ti7-chia beh koh ka7 chu-ui7 kong2 3 hang7-su7, lin2 chiu7 chai ka3 Chu2-jit8-oh8 tu5-khi3 “To7-siong7 kau3-iok8” i2-goa7 bo5 lou7. Beh hou7 lang5 chiap-siu7 Ia5-sou, hou7 lang5 chhin-kin7 Siong7-te3, tek-khak m7 si7 tui3 li2 e5 to5-ia2, koan3-chu3, khe2-hoat, thiu-chhut e5 kang-hu sou2 choe3 e7 kau3 e5 su7. ChhiaN2 li2 chu3-i3 e7-bin7 sou2 kong2. 
  (Goa2 m7 si7 Sin5-hak8-chia2, sou2-i2 goa2 be7 hiau2 kong2 chhim-chhim e5 Sin5-hak8, kau3-li2, a2-si7 sim2-mih8 chou-chit Sin5-hak8, hiah-e5 chhiaN2 niu7 choan-bun5 e5 hak8-chia2 lai5 kong2. Goa2 ti7-chia bu5-kou3 in2 kui2-ku3 Seng3-keng hou7 lan2 khah beng5-pek8 chiah-e5 su7). 
  A. Siong7-te3 kap li2 
  1. Siong7-te3 si7 choat8-tui3 e5 te7-saN-chia2. I m7 si7 goa2, ia7 m7 si7 li2, I si7 eng2-oan2 e5 chun5-chai7, m7 si7 theng3-hau7 li2, goa2 sin3 I, I chiah u7, chiah ti7-teh. Li2 m7 sin3, goa2 m7 sin3, I ia7 eng2-oan2 chun5-chai7. 
  2. Tng lan2 iau2-boe7 chiaN5 heng5 ti7 lau7-bo2 e5 thai-lai7 e5 si5, I chiu7 i2-keng bat lan2, koh ki3 lan2 e5 mia5 ti7 chheh-nih8 (Si-phian 139 phiN). Lan2 it-seng e5 un7-mia7 ti7 I e5 chhiu2-tiong, I long2 m7-bian2 kap li2 chham-siong5, I si7 li2 choat8-tui3 e5 chi-phoe3-chia2. 
  3. Li2 tui3 Siong7-te3 kiam2 e7-tit khong3-gi7 mah? Be7 lah. Lang5 chi2-u7 sun7-hok8, khiam-pi, eng7 iu2-hau3 e5 sim-cheng5 lai5 keng3-pai3 I, ng3-bang7 I lin5-bin2 si-un na7-tiaN7. Siok8-gu2 kong2 “Sun7-thian-chia2 chun5, gek8-thian-chia2 bong5”. Siong7-te3 hou7 li2 be7 bu2-ban7-tit. 
  Na7-si7 an2-ni kiam2-chhai2 li2 beh siuN7 Siong7-te3 si7 chin chan5-jim2 khok-heng5, chu-chu siuN7 beh heng5-hoat8, li7-khui chin hng7. Peng7 m7-si7 an2-ni I thiaN3 se3-kan kau3 chhe I tok8-siN e5 kiaN2 Ia5-sou lai5 chhoe7 lan2. M7 si7 lan2 tai7-seng thiaN3 I, si7 I tai7-seng thiaN3 lan2, koh keng2 lan2. Sou2-i2 chit-e5 o3-biau7 toa7 lah! 
  B. Lun7 chin2-kiu3 
  (1) Chin2-kiu3 si7 tai7-seng chhut-tui3 Pe7 Siong7-te3 sou2 tiaN7-tioh8. Chham-kho2 e7-bin7. 
  A) “I sou2 tai7-seng pi7-pan7 beh tit-tioh8 eng5-kng e5, chiu7-si7 lan2 chiah-e5 hou7 I sou2 tiau3 e5.” (Lo5-ma2 9:23-24). 
  B) “Goa7-pang lang5 thiaN-liau2, chiu7 hoaN-hi2, o-lo2 Siong7-te3 e5 to7-li2; hoan7-na7 siu7 tiaN7-tioh8 beh tit-tioh8 eng2-oah8 e5 lang5 long2 sin3 lah.” (Su3-tou5 13:48). 
  C) “Na7 m7-si7 chhe Goa2 e5 Pe7 in2-chhoa7 i, chiu7 bo5 lang5 oe7 chiu7-kun7 Goa2.” (Iok-han7 6:44). 
  D) “Siong7-te3 chhe I e5 KiaN2 e5 Sin5 jip8 lan2 e5 sim, au5-kio3 kong2, A-pa, Pe7 ah.” (Ka-liap8-thai3 4:6). 
  Tui3 teng2-bin7 kui2-chat Seng3-keng, lan2 chiu7 kho2-i2 beng5-pek8 lang5 e5 tit-kiu3 oan5-choan5 si7 tui3 Pe7 Siong7-te3 e5 u7-sian tiaN7-tioh8 e5 chin2-tiau3 lai5 chiaN5--e5. 
  (2) Chin2-kiu3 si7 chhut tui3 KiaN2 Ia5-sou e5 thiaN3 sou2 si-chhut e5. 
  A) “M7 si7 lin2 keng2 Goa2, si7 Goa2 keng2 lin2, koh siat-lip8 lin2......”. (Iok-han7 15:16). 
  B) “KiaN2 sou2 ai3 beh chi2-si7 e5 i2-goa7, ia7 bo5 chit8 e5 bat Pe7 si7 chi7-chui7.” (Lou7-ka 10:22). 
  (3) Chin2-kiu3 si7 tui3 Seng3 Sin5 e5 kang-chok. 
  A) “Kau3 chin-li2 e5 Sin5 lai5, I beh chhoa7 lin2 jip8 ti7 it-chhe3 e5 chin-li2.......” (Iok-han7 16:13). 
  B) “Chu2 khui i e5 sim, hou7 i choan-sim ng3 Po2-lo5 sou2 kong2 e5 oe7.” (Su3-tou5 Heng7-toan7 16:14). 
  Chong2-kong2 tit-kiu3 m7 si7 tui3 lang5 e5 lou2-lek8, si7 tui3 Siong7-te3 e5 peh8-peh8 e5 un-su3 sou2 tit--e5. 
  I2-hut-sou2 2:8 kong2, “In-ui7 lin2 tui3 un-tian2 tit-tioh8 kiu3, si7 tui3 sin3; che ia7 m7 si7 chhut ti7 lin2 pun2-sin, si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 siuN2-su3.” 
  Lian5 “Sin3-giong2” tou si7 Siong7-te3 siuN2-su3--e5, m7 si7 kong2 li2 siuN7 ai3 sin3 chiu7 e7 sin3. “Sin3” ia7-si7 Siong7-te3 siuN2-su3--e5. 
  Tui3 i2-siong7 e5 li2-iu5 goa2 toan3-teng7 kong2, chong-kau3 kau3-iok8, beh chhoa7 lang5 kau3 ti7 Ia5-sou, hou7 lang5 e7 chiap-siu7 Ia5-sou, tui3 Ia5-sou lai5 bat Pe7 Siong7-te3, chit-e5 su7 tui3 thau5 kau3-boe2 long2 tioh8 oa2-kho3 Seng3 Sin5 e5 lek8-liong7. Lan2 chi2 u7 choe3 khi3-ku7 hou7 Chu2 eng7, lan2 chi2 u7 than3 Chu2 e5 beng7-leng7, chhoa7 se3-kiaN2 lai5 chiu7-kin7 I, na2-chun2 Hui-lek8 chhoa7 Na2-tan3-giap8 kong2 “Lai5 khoaN3”, chiu7-si7 chhoa7 hak8-seng chu3-sin5 khoaN3 Ia5-sou, poe5-phoaN7 hak8-seng saN-kap chau2, pang3 khi3 au7-bin7 tiN5-poaN3, chi2 u7 ng3 teng2-bin7 e5 siuN2 lai5 chau2, chiau3 Chu2 sou2 ui7-tioh8 lan2 sou2 the3 lan2 an-pai5 sou2 tioh8 chau2 e5 lou7. Goa2 kio3 chit-khoan2 e5 kau3-iok8 choe3 “To7-siong7” kau3-iok8. 
  11. Hu3 Chu2-jit8-oh8 kau3-oan5 leng5-siu-hoe7 (4) 
  2. To7-siong7 kau3-iok8 e5 hong-hoat
  TaN lan2 i2-keng chai beh hou7 gin2-na2 tit-tioh8 sin3-giong2, hou7 in e7 chiap-siu7 Ia5-sou, tui3 Ia5-sou Ki-tok hou7 se3-kiaN2 u7 koan5 thang hok8-kui chiaN5 choe3 Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2-ji5, che long2 m7 si7 tui3 lau7-su e5 to5-ia2, koan3-chu3, khe2-hoat, a2-si7 thiu-chhut e5 sou2 e7 thang cho7-chiaN5 e5. Chi2 u7 chiu7-si7 po3 se3-kiaN2 khoaN3 Ia5-sou, chhoa7 se3-kiaN2 lai5 chiu7-kun7 Chu2, hou7 Chu2 chhin-sin ka7 in hoaN7-chhiu2 chiok-hok in ,lan2 chi2 u7 chiu7-si7 chhoa7 in chiuN7 kau3 ti7 Chu2 e5 bin7-cheng5. 
  “Chhoa7 in chiuN7 kau3 ti7 Chu2 e5 bin7-cheng5” chit ku3 chiu7-si7 “To7-siong7” kau3-iok8. 
  TaN li2 siuN7 lan2 beh chaiN2-iuN7 lai5 chhoa7 hak8-seng chiuN7 kau3 Ia5-sou. 
  1. Li2 tioh8 e7 tit tui3 hak8-seng na2-chun2 Hui-lek8 tui3 Na2-tan3-giap8 kong2 an2-ni, kong2, “Mou5-se ki3-tit lut8-hoat kap chiah-e5 sian-ti sou2 ki3 e5, goan2 i2-keng tu2-tioh8 I, chiu7-si7 ...... Ia5-sou.” Te7-it pou7 chiu7-si7 li2 pun2-sin tioh8 seng tu2-tioh8 Ia5-sou. Pa2-ak Ia5-sou, li2 tai7-seng jin7-bat Ia5-sou, tit-tioh8 Ia5-sou. 
  2. Tioh8 chhin-chhiuN7 Po2-lo5 ho2-taN2 kong2, “Lin2 tioh8 oh8 goa2, chhin-chhiuN7 goa2 oh8 Ki-tok.” (I Lim5 11:1). 
  Lang5 siong5-siong5 ai3 kong2 “Lin2 tioh8 chu3-sin5 khoaN3 Ia5-sou, m7-thang khoaN3 goa2”, che si7 to5 chek-jim7 e5 oe7. Ia5-sou ti7 to2-ui7? Lau7-su li2 ti7 hak8-seng e5 bak8-chiu-cheng5, Ia5-sou na7 si7 ho2, li2 tai7-seng oh8 Ia5-sou, hou7 Ia5-sou kiu3-tioh8--e5 tou be7 ho2 lah, beh kio3 goa2 sin3 li2 sou2 kai3-siau7 e5 Ia5-sou, che chin oh. Gin2-na2 lai5 kau3-hoe7, m7 na7 beh khoaN3 lau7-su, bok8-su, tiuN2-lo2, chip-su7, pe7-bo2, hiaN-che2, lian5 pai3-tng5 it-chhe3 e5 heng5-su7 tou si7 in sou2 beh khoaN3, beh hak8-sip8 e5 tui3-siong7. Li2 kong2 Ia5-sou goa7 ho2, thoan5-kau3-chia2 kap tiong2-chip be7 ho5, hoe7-iu2 tu2 hoe7-iu2 oan-ke, Chu2-jit8-oh8 kau3-sek-lai7 lau7-su kong2 sin3 Ia5-sou si7 goa7 ho2, che long2 pian2--e5, bo5 hau7. 
  3. Choe3-au7 e5 hong-hoat chiu7-si7 “ThiaN3”, ti7-chia sou2 kong2 e5 thiaN3 m7 si7 siok8-tek jin5-cheng5 e5 thiaN3: Eros (E-lou-suh) e5 thiaN3. Si7 kong2 siok8-leng5, seng3-kiat, chu3-seng5 e5 thiaN3: Agape (A-ka-pheh) e5 thiaN3, chit-e5 thiaN3 e5 hoat-goan5 chiu7-si7 Siong7-te3. Iok-han7 it-su kong2 “Siong7-te3 chiu7-si7 thiaN3.” Siong7-te3 e5 thiaN3 e5 piau2-hian7 chiu7-si7 chai7 ti7 “chhe I e5 kiaN2 ui7-tioh8 lan2 e5 choe7 choe3 ban2-hoe5 e5 che3.” (I Iok-han7 4:10). Sou2-i2 choe3 lau7-su e5 eng-kai tioh8 u7 Hui-lip8-pi2 2 chiuN sou2 kong2 e5 cheng-sin5, eng7 Chu2 e5 sim choe3 sim, chiu7-si7 “Hoan2-tng2 piaN3-khang ka-ki7, chhu2 lou5-pok8 e5 heng5-chong7, chiaN5 choe3 lang5 e5 iuN7-siuN3, i2-keng u7 chhin-chhiuN7 lang5 e5 khoan2-sit, sun7-hok8 kau3 ti7 si2, sim7-chi3 si2 ti7 sip8-ke3.” Che chiu7-si7 thiaN3 e5 kek8-ti3, seng-hoa, koh-khah ho2 bo5 lah, che chiu7-si7 bu5-siong7 e5 thiaN3. 
  To7-siong7 kau3-iok8-hoat goa2 siuN7 chiu7-si7 an2-ni: (1) Li2, choe3 lau7-su tioh8 ka-ki7 tai7-seng pa2-ak, tit-tioh8 Ia5-sou. (2) Li2 e7 tit ho2-taN2 kio3 hak8-seng, pi7 kau3-iok8-chia2 oh8 li2, chhin-chhiuN7 li2 u7 oh8 Ki-tok. (3) Chiu7-si7 tioh8 the2-thiap Chu2 e5 sim, kam-goan7 chiong li2 e5 si5-kan, cheng-sin5, ti3-sek, seng-khu, siN3-mia7, thou2 oe7 kong2 “ham7-sin kap mia7” long2-chong2 hian3 hou7 Chu2 lai5 ui7-tioh8 hak8-seng. Eng7 chit khoan2 e5 thai3-tou7 lai5 leng2-to7 hak8-seng, in-ui7 goa2 chhim-sin3 beh chhoa7 lang5 kau3 ti7 Chu2, che m7 si7 thau5-khak, heng5-ji5-ha7 e5 kau3-iok8, si7 siok8 ti7 sim-leng5, heng5-ji5-siong7 e5 kau3-iok8, si7 i2 sim hoe7 sim, i2 sin5 hoe7 sin5, jin5-keh-tek kau-liu5 e5 kau3-iok8, si7 tioh8 u7 Chu2 e5 Sin5, Seng3 Leng5 e5 khe2-si7, pang-chan7 chiah e7 thang seng5-kong e5 kau3-iok8. Sou2-i2 na7 m7 si7 pun2-sin u7 chin-chiaN3 tit-tioh8 tui3 teng2-bin7 lai5 e5 lek8-liong7 kap thiaN3-sim ia7 eng7 an2-ni lai5 choe3 chiah-e5 kang, tu5 an2-ni i2-goa7 chiu7 i sou2 choe3 e5 it-chhe3 si7 hong7-heng5 kou3-su7 e5 hu-ian2 na7-tiaN7. Po2-lo5 tui3 Ko-lim5-to lang5 kong2, “Ti7 Ki-tok Ia5-sou, goa2 bat tui3 hok-im lai5 siN lin2, sou2-i2 goa2 khng3 lin2 tioh8 oh8 goa2.” (I Lim5 4:16). Eng7 chit khoan2 e5 sim-cheng5, kap lo5-khou2 lai5 seN sin3-giong2 e5 kiaN2, chit khoan2 lau7-su chiah e7 seng5-kong. 
  Sou2-i2 lau7-su, lan2 tioh8 ka-ki7 tai7-seng chiaN5 choe3 ki5-to2 e5 lang5, m7 na7 si7 choe3 thak8 Seng3-keng sek8-sek8 e5 lang5, kok-khah iau3-kin2 tioh8 chiaN5 choe3 sit8-heng5 Seng3-keng e5 lang5, kan2-tit8 lai5 kong2, lan2 tioh8 choe3 Ia5-sou e5 cheng3-jin5, tui3 Ia5-sou lai5 tit-kiu3, chiaN5-seng3 e5 “Sin5-jin5”, lai5 khia7 ti7 hak8-seng e5 bin7-cheng5. Hou7 hak8-seng tui3 li2 e5 bin7, kap heng5-ui5 lai5 khoaN3-kiN3 Chu2 e5 eng5-kng, an2-ni chiah u7 lat8. An2-ni li2 ku3-ku3 e5 oe7 chiah e7 khap8-tioh8 hak8-seng e5 sim-hian5, thou2-oe7 kong2 “Sim-koaN iN2-a2”, lau5 chhim-khek e5 in3-siong7 ti7 hak8-seng e5 sim-leng5 siong7. Na7 kan-ta hi-hi hoa7-hoa7, kong2 kou3-su7, chhio3-chhio3 leh, liam7 b. ch. chh koa, bok8-koai3 hak8-seng kam2-kak ta-so3 bo5 bi7, kau3 chhou-tiong e5 ni5-leng5, chiu7 khoaN3-khin Chu2-jit8-oh8, choe3 i khi3 bo5 oat8-thau5 lah. 
  Goa2 bat chiong chit khoan2 e5 su7 sio2-khoa2 kai3-siau7 ti7 bou2 Tiong-hoe7 e5 Chu2-jit8-oh8 kau3-oan5 leng5-siu-hoe7 e5 si5, bat hou7 lang5 eng7 leng2-chhio3 lai5 khoaN3-khin, pheng5 kong2 he si7 m7-bat ji5-tong5 sim-li2 e5 kau3-siu7 hoat. Goa2 m7-kaN2 in3 (in-ui7 goa2 chu7-hun7 the3-si5 lah), chong2-si7 chiau3 goa2 e5 keng-giam7 chu7 u7 Tai5-oan5 Chu2-jit8-oh8 kang2-sip8-hoe7 (leng5-siu-hoe7) iok oa2 40 ni5 cheng5 khi2, chiu7-si7 chit khoan2 eng7 khiam-hi-sim, hu7-chek, thiaN3 hak8-seng, chhoa7 in kau3 ti7 Chu2 e5 hong-hoat si7 te7-it ho2. Goa2 m7 si7 kau3-iok8 choan-ka, tai7-ke na7 u7 siuN7-tioh8 koh-khah ho2 e5 hong-hoat, tai7-ke saN-kap lai5 chham-kho2 chin ho2, goa2 ia7 chin hoaN-hi2 tui3 tai7-ke lai5 hak8-sip8 sin-sin e5 kau3-iok8-hak8, kau3-siu7-hoat. 
  TaN chiau3 i2-siong7 sou2 kong2, lan2 lai5 oat8-thau5 khoaN3 lan2 hian7-chai7 e5 Chu2-jit8-oh8, kau3-hoe7 hak8-hau7 e5 kau3-iok8 si7 chaiN2-iuN7? Seng5-kong a2-si7 sit-pai7 ah? 
